 letters, Stephen Ambrose recounts the stories, often in the men\'s own words, of these American heroes.\nForeword\n&quot;We wanted those wings&quot;; Camp Toccoa, 7-12/42\n&quot;Stand up &amp; hook up&quot;; Benning, Mackall, Bragg, Shanks, 12/42-9/43\n&quot;Duties of the latrine orderly&quot;; Aldbourne, 9/43-3/44\n&quot;Look out, Hitler! Here we come!&quot;; Slapton Sands, Uppottery, 4/1-6/5/44\n&quot;Follow me&quot;; Normandy, 6/6/44\n&quot;Move out!&quot;; Carentan, 6/7-7/12/44\nHealing wounds &amp; scrubbed missions; Aldbourne, 7/13-9/16/44\n&quot;Hell\'s highway&quot;; Holland, 9/17-10/1/44\nIsland; Holland, 10/2-11/25/44\nResting, recovering &amp; refitting: Mourmelon-le-Grand, 11/26-12/18/44\n&quot;They got us surrounded-the poor bastards&quot;; Bastogne, 12/19-31/44\nBreaking point; Bastogne, 1/1-13/45 \nAttack; Noville, 1/14-17/45\nPatrol: Haguenau, 1/18-2/23/45\n&quot;Best feeling in the world&quot;: Mourmelon, 2/25-4/2/45\nGetting to know the enemy: Germany, 4/2-30/45\nDrinking Hitler\'s champagne; Berchtesgaden, 5/1-8/45\nSoldier\'s dream life; Austria, 5/8-7/31/45\nPostwar careers; 1945-91\nAcknowledgments &amp; Sources\nIndex<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"16172384802480689806\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'24_book_42389\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"GL0Jr3GNsGtQwwtOhzdbXuFCJye+4I6N6BWabL98Q9MlOzC1CIaRkDr9PMm2LsThTsw1FRi+fPru5q9X7jgibw==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"42389\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"24_book_42389\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/39020.1491\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/span>\n<span class=\'progressIndicator\'>saving…<\/span>\n<\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\'wtrRight wtrUp\'>\n<form class=\"hiddenShelfForm\" action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"JSyahuJ0E1rVBmd3EXyy9K38zR88Dc/n94J8v52vLeYYqqOcm38yob84UPAgZS1LAnLfLZpTPZDxcUmEzOtMWg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"24_book_42389\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"42389\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"a\" id=\"a\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/39020.1491\" />\n<\/form>\n\n<button class=\'wtrShelfButton\'><\/button>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\'ratingStars wtrRating\'>\n<div class=\'starsErrorTooltip hidden\'>\nError rating book. Refresh and try again.\n<\/div>\n<div class=\'myRating uitext greyText\'>Rate this book<\/div>\n<div class=\'c